overview:
Jetmind Technologies is the diversified software development company created to match the rising demand for mobile & web information technology services with winning combination of the top-gun software developers available in Eastern Europe (the Ukraine) and experienced NewYork based management. To generate superior value, Jetmind combines its technological expertise in mobile, web and desktop solutions with the advantages of global delivery. With delivery center in the heart of Europe and office in New York we take full advantage of global understanding of business and superior education and the work ethic of off-shore delivery.

Company has extensive experience in developing custom software and integrated solutions for various business ideas. We provide you not only with a full development cycle services, but with a full quality assurance service, design, and search engine optimization services. We deliver the level of proficiency that you require from an IT company without overcomplicating the process.
